(41864, 6819, 0, 1, '3_Silent Heroes', '這首歌一開始是寫給許許多多在社會專心並默默地做著自己事情的人們，或許他們不能功成名就，但他們都是社會上沈默的英雄。\n\n然而這些年來，我們的社會發生了許許多多不公平，甚至不正一的事情。而幾年之後回來看這首歌，讓我對但丁的一段話又有更深的體悟：\n「地獄的最深處，是保留給那些在道德存亡之際，仍然保持沈默的人。」\n', '2012-01-04 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 7, 'Go go, let them know ‘though all of we do are perfect zero\n\nCome, come, let us show All of us are silent heroes\n\nTo, to see the real Could you see, I am falling\n\nI am falling I am falling\n\n  \n\nYes, yes, as you saw Our bodies become the dirty squirrels\n\nOut, out of the world Our minds flow in the space flow\n\nTo, to see the real Could you see I am falling\n\nI am falling I am falling\n\n\nWith the same voice and the same faces\n\nEveryone and everywhere\n\nyou know\n\nYou know', '', 256, '', 'Under the Moon', 'Under the Moon', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2012-01-04 00:19:24', '2015-03-12 13:49:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
